title: Explore Happiness At Arras!
posting_body: ['Seize the adventure of life at Arras', 'Seize the adventure of life at Arras – centrally located in Bellevue’s up-and-coming Spring District.', 'With three buildings around a courtyard, Arras is a vibrant, welcoming community that offers sophisticated details and quality finishes in bright, airy apartment homes.', 'Minutes from downtown Bellevue and a short trip to Seattle attractions, live at the gateway to the Pacific Northwest’s outdoor paradise, with easy access to the slopes, the surf and everything in between.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 525 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Gas Range *', '- FiberInternet, Direct to Each Apartment', '- Full-Sized, Quality Appliances', '- Open Floor Plan', '- Kitchen Island with Pendant Lighting *', '- Designer Finishes', '- Quartz Countertops', '- Full-Size Washer and Dryer', '- Balcony or Deck *', '*Only available in select units', 'Community Amenities', '- Assigned Parking Available – (additional fee)', '- Courtyard with Landscaping', '- The Lodge: Top-Floor Resident Lounge', '- Permanent Art Installations', '- Pet Washing Station', '- EV Charging Stations Available', '- The Hub + The Perch: Gourmet Kitchen', '- Conference Room & Co-Working Spaces', '- Pedal Club: Game Room with TV & bike Repair Stand', '- Friendly On-Site Management and Maintenance', '- Club Fitness: 2 levels with Peloton, Weights & Cardio', '- Sky Deck: Rooftop Deck with Fire Pit', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Arras', '12282 Northeast 12th Lane, Bellevue, WA, 98005', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'lTlIh6S7SDF']
